text: Kaho, he kitaba vali'o! (Yahudi te isa'i) a'o ika ajihi gala de vala jo sade ate tuhade vica paki hai ki asim alaha tom binham kise di ibadata na kari'e ate alaha de nala kise nu sarika na thahira'i'e. Sade vicom ko'i kise dusare nu alaha de binham raba na bana'e. Phira jekara uha isa tom bacana cahuna tam kahi devo ki tusim gavaha raho asim agi'akari ham
